{
  "stem": "33.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "The only way I could survive, even in the hospital, was that when I had a very high fever, and I couldn't be working, they woke up the night nurse and sent her on the floor while Mengele was inspecting.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And they told him that I'm the night nurse sleeping in the nurses' room, because only one person was allowed to sleep during the day, and that was the one night nurse in the whole hospital.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "So that's the way I survived.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "My cousin was really wonderful.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "She was very brave.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "I assume losing her only child, life didn't matter a lot to her at that time.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "She was the only person who even dared sort of argue, maybe, with Mengele, who didn't just submit to his requests.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "Eventually everybody had to, but she tried her best.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "She worked instead of me when I was sick.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "Her sister was there, too, who is closer to my age.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "She was sick a lot.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "She did her job, too.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "She was stealing potatoes for the patients in the hospital.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "And she did really everything she could.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "She worked a lot.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "I suppose she really buried her sorrow and her terrible sadness, losing her only child in work every day.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "Also she did something that would have cost her life, every time she did it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And I didn't know until later when we came back and she told me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "There were women who were at the very beginning of their pregnancy, maybe they even didn't know that they're pregnant, when they arrived at Auschwitz, and they found out later.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "Performing an abortion was risking your life.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "It was illegal.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "It was not allowed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "It was definitely punishable by death.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
